docs.abstract: China is home to 60 of the world’s 100 tallest buildings now under construction, but the scale and speed of the projects have caused concern; world's tallest building at 202 stories is slated for completion in early 2014 in Changsha after only four months of assembly.

docs.lead_paragraph: Steve Lonegan is waging a campaign to be the first Republican in 40 years elected to the Senate from New Jersey, and he has no intention of letting it be dull.
docs.abstract: Steve Lonegan is waging long-shot campaign to be first Republican in 40 years elected to United States Senate from New Jersey, and he has no intention of letting it be dull; election to replace late Sen Frank R Lautenberg presents stark contrast, with Democratic contender Cory A Booker inviting comparisons to Pres Obama and Lonegan clearly stating his intentions to get to Washington and dismantle the Obama agenda.

headline.main: For Long-Shot New Jersey Senate Candidate, Passion and No Filter
